data.description: Beautiful all-brick ranch ready to become your new home sweet home! Offering an open floorplan, you can comfortably host family and friends in the spacious living room that flows effortlessly into the formal dining room so guests can comfortably mingle. Your home chef doesn’t have to miss a beat in the spacious eat-in kitchen fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of storage space to keep clutter tucked out of sight. The primary bedroom boasts vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with everything you need to begin and end each day in serenity. Located in the Deer Creek neighborhood you can enjoy abundant amenities like a community pool, tennis courts, walking trails, and more! You don’t want to miss this one, schedule your showing today before it’s too late!
